Class SourceRegion

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.wala.cast.js.html.SourceRegion

  • public class SourceRegion
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a region of source code, with source locations. Regions can be added to other SourceRegions, with nested source location information maintained.
